💥🎉 FlexyCoin Preview! Part 4 ( Market Page) 💥🔥! 

Welcome to MarketView! 🚀📈 Get ready to explore a wide variety of coins available in the market. To make your experience super smooth, I've added a special filter section that opens and closes with a stylish animation.

🔍 With these filters, you're in control! You can handpick what you want to see – whether it's based on percentage change or market capacity. Plus, you can choose whether to sort things in ascending or descending order. You can also zoom in on data from the past hour, day, or week, and choose between viewing 50 or 500 items per page.

And guess what? 🎉 You can even create your very own filters based on the API. We've seamlessly integrated these filters into the app.

Oh, and here's a cool trick: by swiping items from left to right, you can easily add them to your favorites list. Stay tuned for a sneak peek of this awesome feature in our upcoming post!

Last but not least, even if your internet connection decides to play hide and seek, our NoInternetConnection view ensures your experience remains glitch-free and uninterrupted on this page. 🌐🚫 Enjoy exploring MarketView!

I'm excited to hear your feedback and hope you love using FlexyCoin. 💬

💥🎉 FlexyCoin Preview! Part 8
( Crypto Filtering ) 💥🔥! 

Step into the Crypto Details View, where you'll discover the magic of "Crypto Filtering." ✨💼 

With just a gentle tap on the AppBar icon, a door to endless possibilities swings open in the form of a delightful BottomSheet. Here, a treasure trove of filtering options awaits your command. 🚪🌟

You have the power to tailor your crypto experience, sifting through the data by Price Change, Market Cap, Volume, or Percent Changes. 📈📊🔄

Once you've sculpted your perfect view, a simple tap on the "Apply Changes" button sends your preferences to the server, summoning fresh data to illuminate your screen. 📡📲✨ And don't forget to bask in the ambiance of dark mode, casting a captivating spell over your exploration. 🌙✨ 

Whether you prefer the enchantment of the night or the clarity of day, this view has it all. 

Happy crypto hunting! 🌟💰🌙🔮🕵️‍♂️

Big thanks for your fantastic support – it means the world to us! 🙌🌟

I have a successful week behind me. I finished this week with all the new features that were included in version 1.1.0, but I also developed a new chart yesterday that will be available in version 1.1.1. The chart will calculate and draw the categories for the currently selected period, where your expense and incomes will be visible. I think this is a very useful chart because it is easy to keep track of how much expense and incomes a category had in the current period.

This 1.1.1 was a quick development because I am planning a new thing in the next period that is not related to 'Future' app. But I'll write about that later. It will be an exciting period.
